SupraDarky, I just want to say: "Thank you for putting this music up. For all the work you put into it. text: I'm alive and well! I went to NYC a couple weeks ago and planned to start working on #1800 right away, but I really felt like I needed a break so I could focus on some personal stuff, mainly work related as it's been very busy (but in a good way!). It's been very good and I hope everyone is enjoying summer (wait, mid-August already? what is this...). I should have the next video up by the end of the week hopefully, I'll start by writing the text. The series and the theme have already been chosen.
